In celebration of the paper s new look, we will be hosting an exhibition in the Woolworths court at the Middelburg Mall.Have a look at photos taken and published over the years, dig through the scratch and take box and see if you find an old photo of yourself, meet the friendly staff and stand a chance to win R1 000 Spar vouchers.For a chance to win a Spar voucher, either post a selfie of yourself and your friends or family with the new look Middelburg Observer in the background onto Facebook, Instagram or Twitter using #NewLookObserver.Or answer an easy question and fill in your details found in the Friday 3 March and Tuesday 7 March edition of the Middelburg Observer, then drop the forms into the box at the exhibition and wait for your phone to ring.&nbsp;